{"tid":590293,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"見就黎到dse...有樣野想提提動物台手足...","createTime":"2018-03-12T13:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T07:53:18.000Z","uid":8307,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0ab876e234be9a83846c959aa83aebbb4d01b8","tid":590293,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"話說細佬我當年考公開試...<br />\n帶咗老婆隻膠人入試場考...<br />\n拎出黎放係枱面係咁比人笑...太緊張唔小心掃左隻膠人落地下<br />\n隻斷左佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多得佢我現今係美帝常春藤畢業,做緊家族公司既高層...<br />\n我到到依家都冇望記隻膠人,一直掛住咗佢個頭係office到提醒自己...<br />\n希望各位手足唔好成日轉老婆..."},{"pid":"d0b7723db5f72359526dac80047bb4af866eab5a","tid":590293,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"唔好再回哩個垃圾post 再回死全家"},{"pid":"3543ba29e7fc473d8b86693367f6d0ccbe88b0b9","tid":590293,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0b7723db5f72359526dac80047bb4af866eab5a","tid":590293,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"唔好再回哩個垃圾post 再回死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"回 你死全家"},{"pid":"9f03bc137aad5f03cbf16477234939c3bdf0aa50","tid":590293,"uid":2794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"5532113852bc5b7c7c176c7e8e2e4d1c1999c54a","tid":590293,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f03bc137aad5f03cbf16477234939c3bdf0aa50","tid":590293,"uid":2794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"你唔記得左山風 死全家"},{"pid":"915f1aafc46f34c93055bd27782a10962573a8d6","tid":590293,"uid":2794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5532113852bc5b7c7c176c7e8e2e4d1c1999c54a","tid":590293,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f03bc137aad5f03cbf16477234939c3bdf0aa50","tid":590293,"uid